revisions.rev:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''American Idol'' episodes}}
The following is a list of episodes for the [[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]] reality series '''''[[American Idol]]'''''. The series debuted in the United States on June 11, 2002.

