 |ShortSummary=[[Rod Stewart]] performs "[[The Way You Look Tonight]]." The remaining finalists except for [[Taylor Hicks]] (who is announced to be the highest vote-getter) are split into two groups. The far right group consists of [[Chris Daughtry]], [[Ace Young]], and [[Paris Bennett]]. The far left group consists of [[Elliott Yamin]], [[Katharine McPhee]], and [[Kellie Pickler]]. Hicks is asked to join the group he thinks is the top three. He starts to walk toward [[Chris Daughtry|Chris]]' group but when Ryan Seacrest tells him he's wrong, Hicks immediately shakes hands with Daughtry and goes to the other group instead. It is announced that Daughtry's group is the bottom three, and Ace Young is eliminated.
